title: Foster and Farry announce 800 Teleperformance jobs in Fermanagh (Department of Finance and Personnel)
text: ( Source : Department of Finance and Personnel ) Finance Minister Arlene Foster MLA , and Employment and Learning Minister , Dr Stephen Farry today announced that Teleperformance intends to create 800 new jobs in Enniskillen , Fermanagh ~
